msgid ""
"For example, appending "
"<code>?source_entity_type=node&source_entity_id=1</code> to a "
"webform's URL would set a submission's 'Submitted to' value to "
"'node:1'."
msgstr ""
"Por exemplo, ao adicionar "
"<code>?source_entity_type=node&source_entity_id=1</code> à URL de um "
"webform, o valor de “Enviado para” do envio seria definido como "
"“node:1”."

